self.preprocess(image_path)
print('Found {} outputs'.format(len(self.model)))
for output in self.model:
    predict = output.eval({output.arguments[0]: [self.data / 255.0]})
    predict.dump('finalconv_{}.npy'.format(str(predict.shape[1])))
    print('The output of CNTK model file is saved as [finalconv_{}.npy].'.
        format(str(predict.shape[1])))
print('generated by [{}.py], [{}] and [{}].'.format(self.args.n, self.args.
    w, image_path))
